		<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/35eb05c30f27676e12685d2f2d69bba4?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
